"FactDragon79"                             = "The «Gorynych» dragon’s blood is so thick the Earth itself refuses to swallow it.";
"FactDragon80"                             = "Some medieval «dragon» sightings were actually just displays of the Aurora Borealis.";
"FactDragon81"                             = "The «Wyrm» is a dragon that has no legs or wings and moves like a giant earthworm.";
"FactDragon82"                             = "In some folklore, dragons can be repelled by the juice of a wild lemon.";
